<!-- COPY PANEL -->
<p>
<h2>Our Vision</h2>
Hospitality Guru's vision is to share the knowledge, experience and passion of its founder, Jean Muller, with the South African service industry.

</p>
<p>
<h2>Our Goal</h2>
Hospitality Guru's primary goal is to assist establishments in the South African service industry to achieve their specific goals: short-term and long-term, financial and operational.
</p>
<p>
<h2>Achieving our Goal</h2>
<i>Knowledge</i> - shared through quality consulting.<br>
<i>Experience</i> - passed on by hands-on training.<br>

<i>Passion</i> - expressed in the way Hospitality Guru operates.<br>
</p>
